Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zeff and Sanji's Dream;\NThe Illusory All Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how incredible he was\Nin the past, he's now a mere cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to blow his brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save this man,\Nright, Sanji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, leave the ship without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, do you look stupid,\Nyou damn geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're like that, you can't set\Na good example for the fighting cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I don't need a lecture\Nfrom a little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get off calling me\N"little brat," you damn bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit treating me like a kid already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure isn't gonna\Nforsake Owner, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! Point that gun at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die so bad,\NI'll kill you in a refined way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:03:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move if you don't want\Nyour Owner's head blown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Absolutely Natural Pearl... Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Why aren't you dodging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, that damn underling\Nwould pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? If you abandon this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's life will be saved.\NIt's a no-brainer, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This restaurant is that\Ndamn geezer's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took everything away\Nfrom that damn geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I don't want that damn\Ngeezer to lose anything else!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Watch out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl... Cymbals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The All Blue?\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a legendary sea.\NIt's definitely out there somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! Though there\Nis a legend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're seafaring cooks, so we've\Nall dreamed of that sea at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I'll definitely\Nfind that sea some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you'll find it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what kind of place\Nthe All Blue is to start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do! Don't insult my intelligence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The East Blue, West Blue,\NNorth Blue, and South Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea where fish from\Nall four seas live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the All Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To seafaring cooks,\Nthat's an irresistible paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! There's all sorts of seafood\Nfrom all over the world in that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooks would be itching for\Nthe chance to show their skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's worth risking your\Nlife to look for that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That is, if such a sea exists...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a miracle sea\Nlike the All Blue could exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious if you just\Ngive it a little thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a big lie told by some\Ndaydreaming cook somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, enough with the silly stories.\NGo collect plates, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... How wasteful...\Nleaving this much food...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one has barely been touched.\NI was sure they'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Customers these days\Nsure are pampered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stop eating\Nthe customers' leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ditched food that\Nlooked rotten earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying things like that shows you're\Nstill just halfway to being a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget we're seafaring cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is an unpredictable place,\Nso it's best not to waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have some, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please calm\Ndown! Calm down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ship is... The Cook Pirates...\NRed Foot Zeff's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they came back\Nfrom the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you're the pirate captain\NRed Foot Zeff. How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steal all the valuables from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm not gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna be killed\Nby bastards like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid. Don't swing things\Nlike that around. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bleeding. It's a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm not gonna be killed\Nby bastards like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji!\N--Stop it! Don't fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he's got a death wish.\NKill that brat already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die! If I'm\Ngonna be killed by you bastards,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boy, you did it, Captain.\N--You have no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will find the All Blue some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "All Blue"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an ambitious goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, tell him... that it didn't\Nexist even in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He's still\Nspouting that nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna be killed by damn\Npirates in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Let's withdraw!\NThis storm is bigger than we expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! Hurry up\Nand take the treasure on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're withdrawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji!\N--Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that for just one brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come to, little brat?\NYou're very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can move!\NWhose kicks do you think you took?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? The sea was very rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if\Nthey were completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones\Nwho washed up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no fruits or animals\Non this rocky mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're at least fish in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since the rock has\Nbeen curved by the waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to come back up\Nonce we go down. Isn't that sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! It's all your fault!\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep complaining. We have no\Nchoice but to wait for help anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If no one comes, we'll just\Ndry up and turn into skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skeleton?! I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bag over there is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the food that\Nluckily washed up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 5 days worth of food\Nat most if you eat normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head and eat.\NGood thing that we're both cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Is that your share?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge... at least three\Ntimes as large as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm an adult.\NMy stomach is larger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful that\NI'm even sharing food with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect any pity from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You watch the other side of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you see a ship, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we won't be in contact at all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because that'd be a waste of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let him\Nknow even if I see a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.\NI have 5 days worth of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have 5 days, there'll definitely\Nbe a ship or two passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just in case, I'll divide\Nthem up for 20 days for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have 20 days, there'll\Nbe a ship passing by for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.\NI'll definitely survive. It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No ship passed by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I'll just have to\Nbe patient for a couple more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last piece of bread...\NIt's gotten moldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... How wasteful...\Nleaving this much food...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stop eating\Nthe customers' leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ditched food that\Nlooked rotten earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have some, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My last piece of bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... if that damn\Ngeezer already died...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's food, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that much food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all his fault to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for,\Nlittle brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a ship or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to steal your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can kill me, go ahead.\NI'll die if I don't eat anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you to have this\Nmuch food all to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that we wouldn't\Nbe in contact until we saw a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? This is all treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd that we can't eat\Nwhen we have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:18:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... This bag is filled with treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!\NWhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your food?\NYou didn't eat anything until today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't a dream...\NIn order to save me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the food? Did you\Ngive me all the food you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that leg, you won't be\Nable to be a pirate any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any reason\Nfor you to be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...\Nyou had the same dream as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... even your men\Nsaid it doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes,\Nhead to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The All Blue surely exists there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, I can't be a pirate any more,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time, you can go and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Geezer, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just do as you please\Nand die as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many people\Ndied cursing the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the grandness of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've experienced crises like\Nthis where I couldn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And each time I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that there was a restaurant\Nin the middle of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was thinking that if\NI could leave this place alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd build a restaurant as\Nmy final purpose in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I'll help\Nyou do that. So don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! It's impossible for\Na weak little brat like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!! Help the geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help the damn geezer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!! Hey!! Hey!!...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn geezer gave up\Nhis leg so that I could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't repay the damn\Ngeezer for his kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless I risk my life for him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get up... Sanji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for this place to be\Na restaurant as long as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...\NIs he trying to get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! That's such a refined line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this restaurant will be closed now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it will change into a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you idiot!\NKeep your hands off of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they call themselves the\Nstrongest pirate group in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was just because they had so many\Npirates. That's all. Right, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk very candidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. It seems like Ghin\Ncan't defeat Sanji, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're those weapons that\Nlook like skewered dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't an underling?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coolheaded, Coldhearted Demon;\NPirate Fleet Chief Commander Ghin"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
